item.title: 关于／About
item.description: 欢迎访问我的博客。 Thanks for visiting! I am a master student in computer science at Northeastern University. This site will aggregate my scattered online presence and hopefully provide a place for recording what I learn. 自我介绍 我目前是东北大学计算机与信息科学学院的在读硕士研究
